      "content": "\"take a break from the world entirely\" ... that's exactly what i'm thinking. like, what does that even look like? because everything feels so permanent and heavy. it feels like everyone else has this roadmap for life, but for me, the road just ends. is there actually any point in trying to fix a life that everyone else has already decided is broken?",
